<p>
<note n="0139001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0139001">本文 santi 為 saṁkhari？</note>
<note n="0139002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0139002">於此處舍利堂是 cetiyaghara（支提堂、廟堂）。</note>
<note n="0139003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0139003">本文 pūjayī 為 pūjayo？</note>
<note n="0140004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0140004">本文 vara 為 gavara？</note>
<note n="0141005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0141005">本文 pasuro 為 sasuro？</note>
<note n="0141006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0141006">原語 Kaniṭṭhatissa 是弟提沙之意。</note>
<note n="0142007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142007">原語 Lohapāsada 是（銅殿）前出。</note>
<note n="0142008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142008">本文 patiṭṭhasi 是 patiṭṭhapi？</note>
<note n="0142009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142009">本文 dīpanti 是 dipenti？</note>
<note n="0142010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142010">本文 bhikkhu dūsentaṁ 是 bhikkhū dūsente？</note>
<note n="0142011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142011">本文 Hatthapaṇhihi pāsānaṁ 為 Hattha-（or Satta-）paṇṇikapāsā-daṃ？</note>
<note n="0142012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142012">本文 pāsādikaṁ 是 pāsādakaṁ。</note>
<note n="0143013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0143013">又可讀為 Saṁghatisso？</note>
<note n="0144014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0144014">本文 ubhosamaggabhāvissaṁ upasampadaṁ gabbha-vīsaṁ（or vīse）（Vinaya Text Mahāvagga P. 93）。（I, 75 參照）</note>
<note n="0144015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0144015">本文 dantagaṇikā 是 dandhagaṇika？</note>
<note n="0144016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0144016">本文 bahu 是 bahū。</note>
<note n="0145017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0145017">本文 vāsi 是 vāpi？</note>
</p>
